Redesign activity presentation — each mode shows only relevant spots

Problem: SpotRanker showed paragliding sites to kiters, fishing lakes
to paragliders, etc. TodayHero was a vague "Active Now" button list.

Fixes:
- SpotRanker: hard filter by activity — kiting only sees kite spots,
  paragliding only sees PG sites, fishing only sees lakes
- LakeSelector: kiting/windsurfing no longer see 35 fishing lakes
- TodayHero: completely rebuilt as Activity Recommender grid showing
  every activity with GO/WAIT/OFF status, the WHY (conditions),
  and window timing — tap any card to jump into that activity
- Dashboard: PotM direction ranges updated to match widened 110-250
- Footer trial text: removed hardcoded "7 Days"
